{"tid":443812,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［Ps4] Fifa Pro club D1 隊招攻擊球員","createTime":"2017-10-22T03:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T11:42:35.000Z","uid":28812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"327cb19f798d4a531a8f692790dc29d51076cbf1","tid":443812,"uid":28812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T03:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/22/104315_e31ddb530eb28a7801862512db78333c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F22%2F104315_e31ddb530eb28a7801862512db78333c.jpg&h=40634a03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隊名： Split Force （成立咗5年嘅鳩隊）<br />\n風格 ：永不開咪 ，無人會叫你要點踢點打 。可以盡情發揮自己嘅Club<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，可以一齊靜靜地打下機嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （有時打成晚成隊波一句whatsapp msg都無）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近況 ：目前d1 ，長打嘅隊員大概 5-6 人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n招人：前中後都收，每日開波 。<br />\n對隊友唯一要求 ：肯夾肯就 ，人多就打下其他位置 。<br />\n打前嘅應傳就傳 ，打後嘅做返應該做嘅嘢就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔駛好波 ，我地驚咗「高手」，怕咗「教練」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一班人肯一齊贏一齊輸就得 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有意者可留psn ,或加我 psn :<br />\nTorcidahk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n理念相同夾到嘅可入wahtsapp group ，入得就長玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不收pt 人士 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝收睇 。"},{"pid":"e4ba6563a686942cbfd5f609263ad9d8d2a2db65","tid":443812,"uid":28812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T03:05:53.000Z","msg":"今日都有波開 ，可join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmo